### Holiday API

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Get holidays by year
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/holidays/2026

### Get holidays by year and month
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/holidays/2026/2

### Get holidays by date
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/holidays/2026/2/16

### Create single holiday
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/holidays
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "holidayDate": "2027-01-01",
  "name": "신정"
}

### Create bulk holidays
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/holidays/bulk
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "holidays": [
    { "holidayDate": "2027-02-08", "name": "설날" },
    { "holidayDate": "2027-02-09", "name": "설날" },
    { "holidayDate": "2027-02-10", "name": "설날" },
    { "holidayDate": "2027-03-01", "name": "삼일절" }
  ]
}

### Update holiday (replace {id} with actual id)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/holidays/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "holidayDate": "2026-02-16",
  "name": "설날 (수정)"
}

### Delete holiday (replace {id} with actual id)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/holidays/1
